	</div>

	<div>
		<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<div class="p-4">
				<video controls class="img-fluid" style="border-radius:10px;">
					<source src="video/yoga%20v01.mp4" " type="video/mp4">
           
				</video>
			</div>
		</div>

			<div class="col-md-6 ">

			<div class="p-3">
			<h4 class="justify-content-center text-center  text-black " >Benefit Of Yoga</h4>
			<p class="p-0 m-0 form-text text-center text-dark">Yoga offers comprehensive benefits for overall well-being, including improved flexibility, strength, posture, and circulation, while boosting immunity and reducing inflammation. Mentally, it reduces stress, enhances clarity, improves sleep, and boosts mood. Emotionally, yoga fosters stability, connection, self-confidence, and self-care. Holistically, it balances energy levels, integrates body and mind, and supports spiritual growth. This makes yoga a valuable practice for physical health, mental clarity, emotional balance, and holistic wellness. </p>
			</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>










